{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Description</h2>MechaLeague is a fast-paced online VR platformer that uses grab and pull locomotion, grapple hooks and air brakes.<br>Easy to learn but difficult to master, compete with other players on PC and mobile VR headsets and desktop to score the most points and fastest race times.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/420760/extras/LobbyLoop_01.gif?t=1725080267\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Triple Trials</h2>Currently the game has 2 game modes, Triple Trials and Custom Challenge.<br>You will then play a 3 round match consisting of randomised levels from a rotating pool.<br>Rounds consists of races, orb grab and bomb tag games<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/420760/extras/LevelBanner_01.gif?t=1725080267\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Custom Challenge Maps</h2>You can also create your own custom maps filled with platforms and obstacles. <br>Browse all the maps made by other players and compete for the best times on each map.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cosmetics</h2>After a Triple Trials match you will earn XP which will unlock player cosmetics.<br>Customise every part of your avatar.<br>Contains both free cosmetics and premium cosmetics DLC<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/420760/extras/CustomisationLoop_01.gif?t=1725080267\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Play Triple Trials","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/420760/deee63588c0e5953fbbc1f89826cd892026f7cbc.jpg"},{"name":"Upload Custom Map","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/420760/e805117caddfd0b3b13ce8307066877f7c1f2ff4.jpg"},{"name":"Rate a Map","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/420760/c4e8532dc3c36d97d6741fbc2d4bfe68741b14eb.jpg"},{"name":"Tier 10","path":